series.name: Active Listings in Florida
series.description: This chart shows the number of active real estate listings in Florida. A higher number indicates more properties are available for sale.

series.name: Median Days on Market in Florida
series.description: This chart displays the median number of days that properties stay on the market before being sold. A lower value suggests faster sales.

series.name: Active Listing Count Month-Over-Month in Florida
series.description: The count of active single-family and condo/townhome listings for a given market during the specified month (excludes pending listings).
